                     <interp inst="t18000917-104-off561" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000917-104-off561" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000917-104-cd562" type="crimeDate">19th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000917-104-off561 t18000917-104-cd562"></join>, a silver watch, value 20s. and a gold seal, value 5s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18000917-104-victim992" type="victimName">
                  Mary 
                  Duffey
               <interp inst="t18000917-104-victim992" type="surname" value="Duffey"></interp>
